query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `goalTemplates` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `categoryId` int NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `targetType` enum('tecnica','comportamental','lideranca','resultado','desenvolvimento') NOT NULL,
  `metrics` json,
  `suggestedActions` json,
  `suggestedDurationMonths` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `difficultyLevel` enum('basico','intermediario','avancado') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'intermediario',
  `usageCount` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `successRate` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `active` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  `createdBy` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `goalTemplates_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
